{
  "stem": "3382.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was the first time that they saw a tractor on, on the Zapole Estate.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And it-- and it-- and we started to thresh grain.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And as-- to guard the tractor and the thresher, they, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they sent three policemen and a German soldier-- four people.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The thresher-- the tractor kept kept broke-- to break down-- two or three times.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So whatever had to be done in three or four days lasted and lasted into-- you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The very first day when they came, I-- the very first day when they came, I took Sula and took her to a safe place, to a village called Rulewicze about 10 kilometers, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] probably south or southwest from, from the place where we were, Zapole.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But when I came back, I told that she and Zarek went to her friend's, to village [NON-ENGLISH], which was just on the opposite side, you know, opposite side of Lida.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "One day, one of the-- I was working in grading tomatoes, the policeman came up and started to play with the revolver, and so on, talking about this and that, and whatever it is.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he says, and I had the very good relations with the villages-- village people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I went, you know, and I matched a couple there, who with full Polish customs, whatever or not.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he came, you know, he tells me-- you know, he tells me with a, a smile-- I was in working clothes-- he said, you look like a Jewish butcher.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "God, I heard that, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, you know, I was-- I almost dropped dead.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't know what to do.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I looked at him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I look at him.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
